<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-15-0027 </DOCNO><TEXT>The quantities introduced by ICRU for the radiological monitoring arecommented, specially those implied in individual protection against externalphotons. A procedure is proposed in order to standardize the individualdosemeters by using the kerma in air references of CIEMAT-JEN. The referenceradiation beams are described in connection with ISO standards. Provisionalvalues are selected for the appropriate conversion and correction factors.(author). 14 figs., 23 refs.</TEXT></DOC>